HEADWORD: Trawler
<hw>Trawl"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, trawls.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A fishing vessel which trails a net behind
it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trawlerman</ent>⟦br⟧
